WHO WE ARE

About Vitalgenza

Vitalgenza is a forward-thinking healthcare initiative dedicated to exploring new ideas at the intersection of medicine, research, and technology. Built on curiosity, global exposure, and a passion for service, Vitalgenza aims to contribute to the evolution of healthcare by encouraging innovation, collaboration, and practical learning experiences.

MEET THE FOUNDER

About the Founder

Founder & Innovator

Shrihan Palicherla

Founder & Healthcare Innovator

Shrihan Palicherla is the founder of Vitalgenza and a globally minded student driven by a passion for medicine, innovation, and making a positive impact. After moving from North Carolina, USA to Bangalore, India in 2024, Shrihan developed a unique global perspective shaped by experiences across both countries.

A two-time national badminton champion, national-level coach, and school team captain, Shrihan brings discipline, leadership, and resilience into every pursuit. He is a driven IB Diploma Programme student and an aspiring physician who has completed coursework in human anatomy and physiology from top institutions.

Through clinical internships, volunteering at medical clinics, and active community service, Shrihan has gained firsthand exposure to patient care and the realities of modern healthcare. Vitalgenza was founded to channel this experience into meaningful innovation, with the goal of developing future medical technologies that improve lives worldwide.
